metadata.name: Loneliness
metadata.description:
Loneliness is a cold and bitter wind  
That howls through the empty halls of the heart,  
Whipping up doubts and fears within,  
Leaving one feeling lost and apart.

Hope, though, is a spark that flickers bright,  
A flame that burns within the soul,  
A promise of a better day and night,  
A beacon that guides toward a whole.


film photography,  
april, 2022.
